text: Two ships of the Royal Fleet Auxiliary have borne the name RFA Olwen: * RFA Olwen was an oiler launched in 1917 as . She was renamed RFA Olwen in 1937 and was sold in 1947. * was an oiler launched in 1964 as RFA Olynthus. She was renamed RFA Olwen in 1967 and was sold in 2001.
